Release Notes for Version 3.11.4
================================

Overview
--------

Release 3.11.4 is the fifth release in Errata Tool 3.11. It closes [11
bugs and RFEs][buglist].

This release's highlights include support for adding bugs to advisories
without moving them immediately to ON_QA, Product Security approval workflow
enhancements, released package validations, and further performance
improvements for advisories with large file lists.

